         <div type="translation">
            <p>Aurelia Flavia Antonia Elpis, daughter of Neikias, by birth of Italikos (buried) Marcus
               Aurelius Apolloniοs son of Andron (son of Andron son of Andron), <foreign xml:lang="la">eques</foreign>,
     chief-doctor, her own husband, in memoriam. </p>
         </div>
